#. [campaign]: id=The Deceivers Gambit 1
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/_main.cfg:149
msgid ""
"Yearning for adventure, a newly-trained apprentice from the magic academy at "
"Alduin fights alongside Wesnoth’s king during a major war against the orcs "
"of the north.\n"
"\n"
"Play a pivotal role during this time of turmoil, as despite a string of "
"battlefield victories Wesnoth seems to be slipping inexorably into chaos...\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"Auf der Suche nach Abenteuern kämpft ein frisch ausgebildeter Lehrling der "
"Magieakademie von Alduin an der Seite des Königs von Wesnoth in einem großen "
"Krieg gegen die Orks des Nordens.\n"
"\n"
"Spielt in dieser Zeit des Umbruchs eine Schlüsselrolle, denn trotz einer "
"Serie gewonnener Schlachten scheint Wesnoth unaufhaltsam ins Chaos "
"abzugleiten…\n"
"\n"

#. [campaign]: id=The Deceivers Gambit 1
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/_main.cfg:153
msgid "(Intermediate level, 7 scenarios.)"
msgstr "(Mittlerer Schwierigkeitsgrad, 7 Szenarien.)"

#. [campaign]: id=The Deceivers Gambit 1
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/_main.cfg:155
msgid ""
"The saga continues in\n"
"<i>The Deceiver’s Gambit II</i>"
msgstr ""
"Die Saga geht weiter in\n"
"<i>Das Gambit der Lügen II</i>"

#. [campaign]: id=The Deceivers Gambit 2
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/_main.cfg:164
msgid "The Deceiver’s Gambit II"
msgstr "Das Gambit der Lügen II"

#. [campaign]: id=The Deceivers Gambit 2
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/_main.cfg:177
msgid ""
"As losses continue to mount, Delfador embarks on a dangerous mission behind "
"enemy lines. The journey will be perilous, but what awaits at its end will "
"be worse still. What does it truly mean to be a hero?\n"
"    \n"
msgstr ""
"Angesichts steigender Verluste begibt sich Delfador auf eine gefährliche "
"Mission hinter den feindlichen Linien. Die Reise ist voller Gefahren, doch "
"was am Ende auf ihn wartet, wird noch schlimmer sein. Was heißt es wirklich, "
"ein Held zu sein?\n"
"    \n"

#. [campaign]: id=The Deceivers Gambit 2
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/_main.cfg:179
msgid "(Intermediate level, 8 scenarios.)"
msgstr "(Mittlerer Schwierigkeitsgrad, 8 Szenarien.)"

#. [campaign]: id=The Deceivers Gambit 2
#. this campaign is not a direct continuation of the story and characters, but is next chronologically and is the recommended next campaign
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/_main.cfg:182
msgid ""
"The saga continues in\n"
"<i>Liberty</i>"
msgstr ""
"Die Saga geht weiter in\n"
"<i>Freiheit</i>"

#. [achievement_group]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/achievements.cfg:21
msgid "Blast the fire elementals in <i>Graduation</i>."
msgstr "Lasst die Feuerelementare in <i>Die Abschlussprüfung</i> hochgehen."

#. [achievement_group]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/achievements.cfg:21
msgid "Scenario 0: Sandbagger"
msgstr "Szenario 0: Sandsack"

#. [achievement_group]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/achievements.cfg:22
msgid "Complete <i>Stirrings of War</i> without killing any goblin spearmen."
msgstr ""
"Schließt <i>Rauch am Horizont</i> ab, ohne einen einzigen Kobold-Speerträger "
"zu töten."

#. [achievement_group]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/achievements.cfg:22
msgid "Scenario 1: Goblinitarian"
msgstr "Szenario 1: Koboldfreund"

#. [achievement_group]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/achievements.cfg:23
msgid "Complete the hidden victory condition in <i>Fort Garard</i>."
msgstr "Schließt die geheime Siegbedingung in <i>Festung Garard</i> ab."

#. [achievement_group]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/achievements.cfg:23
msgid "Scenario 2: Bloodthirsty"
msgstr "Szenario 2: Blutdürstig"

#. [achievement_group]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/achievements.cfg:24
msgid "Complete <i>The Ambassador</i> without killing any wose."
msgstr ""
"Schließt <i>Der Botschafter</i> ab, ohne einen einzigen Waldschrat zu töten."

#. [achievement_group]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/achievements.cfg:24
msgid "Scenario 3: Mellon"
msgstr "Szenario 3: Mellon"

#. [achievement_group]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/achievements.cfg:25
msgid "Drown the silverback in <i>The Sylvan Seer</i>."
msgstr "Ertränkt den Silberrücken in <i>Die Seherin des Waldes</i>."

#. [achievement_group]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/achievements.cfg:25
msgid "Scenario 4: Gurgle gurgle"
msgstr "Szenario 4: Gluck gluck"

#. [achievement_group]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/achievements.cfg:26
msgid "Defeat both enemy leaders in <i>The Deceiver</i> before Garard does."
msgstr ""
"Besiegt beide feindlichen Anführer in <i>Der Winkelzug</i>, bevor Garard es "
"tut."

#. [achievement_group]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/achievements.cfg:26
msgid "Scenario 5: Hook, Line, and Sinker"
msgstr "Szenario 5: Haken, Leine und Senker"

#. [achievement_group]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/achievements.cfg:27
msgid "Complete <i>Ring of Swords</i> with Garard at full hp."
msgstr "Schließt <i>Ring der Schwerter</i> ab, während Garard volle LP hat."

#. [achievement_group]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/achievements.cfg:27
msgid "Scenario 6: Royal Privilege"
msgstr "Szenario 6: Königliches Vorrecht"

#. [achievement_group]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/achievements.cfg:28
msgid "Complete <i>The Great River</i> in 20 turns or less."
msgstr "Schließt <i>Der Große Fluss</i> in 20 Runden oder weniger ab."

#. [achievement_group]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/achievements.cfg:28
msgid "Scenario 7: On the Clock"
msgstr "Szenario 7: Auf die Minute"

#. [achievement_group]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/achievements.cfg:29
msgid ""
"Complete <i>Ruins of Saurgrath</i> on the same turn you’re first spotted."
msgstr ""
"Schließt <i>Ruinen von Saurgrath</i> in derselben Runde ab, in der Ihr zum "
"ersten Mal entdeckt werdet."

#. [achievement_group]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/achievements.cfg:29
msgid "Scenario 8: Monster in the Mist"
msgstr "Szenario 8: Monster im Nebel"

#. [achievement_group]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/achievements.cfg:30
msgid "Complete <i>Omaranth</i> before turns run out."
msgstr "Schließt <i>Omaranth</i> ab, bevor das Rundenlimit erreicht ist."

#. [achievement_group]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/achievements.cfg:30
msgid "Scenario 9: Sapper"
msgstr "Szenario 9: Pionier"

#. [achievement_group]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/achievements.cfg:33
msgid "Command four ghosts at once in <i>Houses of the Dead</i>."
msgstr "Befehligt gleichzeitig vier Geister in <i>Häuser der Toten</i>."

#. [achievement_group]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/achievements.cfg:33
msgid "Scenario 10: Army of the Dead"
msgstr "Szenario 10: Armee der Toten"

#. [achievement_group]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/achievements.cfg:35
msgid "Complete <i>Clan Blackcrest</i> in 10 turns or less."
msgstr "Schließt <i>Der Schwarzgipfel-Clan</i> in 10 Runden oder weniger ab."

#. [achievement_group]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/achievements.cfg:35
msgid "Scenario 11: Combined Arms"
msgstr "Szenario 11: Vereinte Kräfte"

#. [achievement_group]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/achievements.cfg:36
msgid "Destroy all three enemy keeps in <i>The Traitor</i>."
msgstr "Zerstört alle drei feindlichen Burgen in <i>Der Verräter</i>."

#. [achievement_group]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/achievements.cfg:36
msgid "Scenario 12: Scorched Earth"
msgstr "Szenario 12: Verbrannte Erde"

#. [achievement_group]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/achievements.cfg:37
msgid "Defeat all enemy leaders in <i>Revelry, Revisited</i>."
msgstr "Besiegt alle feindlichen Anführer in <i>Nach dem Siegesfest</i>."

#. [achievement_group]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/achievements.cfg:37
msgid "Scenario 13: Stand Fast"
msgstr "Szenario 13: Niemals aufgebeen"

#. [achievement_group]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/achievements.cfg:38
msgid ""
"Complete the first phase of <i>Long Live the Queen</i> without moving "
"Delfador."
msgstr ""
"Schließt die erste Phase von <i>Es lebe die Königin</i> ab, ohne Delfador zu "
"bewegen."

#. [achievement_group]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/achievements.cfg:38
msgid "Scenario 14: Armchair General"
msgstr "Szenario 14: Schaukelstuhl-General"

#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/lua/skill_set.lua:7
msgid "Attack:"
msgstr "Angriff:"

#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/lua/skill_set.lua:8
msgid "Spell:"
msgstr "Zauber:"

#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/lua/skill_set.lua:9
msgid "Passive:"
msgstr "Passiv:"

#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/lua/skill_set.lua:20
msgid "Magic Missile"
msgstr "Magisches Geschoss"

#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/lua/skill_set.lua:22
msgid "Ranged 7x3 fire, <i><ref dst='weaponspecial_magical'>magical</ref></i>."
msgstr ""
"Fernkampf, 7x3 Feuer, <i><ref dst='weaponspecial_magical'>Magischer Angriff</"
"ref></i>."

#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/lua/skill_set.lua:29
msgid "Shield"
msgstr "Schild"

#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/lua/skill_set.lua:31
msgid ""
"Spend <span color='#00bbe6' style='italic'>8 XP</span> to gain an additional "
"<i>20% terrain defense</i> (chance to evade) until the start\n"
"          of your next turn or until cancelled."
msgstr ""
"Opfert <span color='#00bbe6' style='italic'>8 EP</span>, um bis zum Beginn "
"Eures nächsten Zuges oder bis zur Aufhebung zusätzliche\n"
"          <i>20% Geländeverteidigung</i> (Chance zum Ausweichen) zu erhalten."

#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/lua/skill_set.lua:39
msgid "Panacea"
msgstr "Wunderheilung"

#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/lua/skill_set.lua:41
msgid ""
"Spend <span color='#00bbe6' style='italic'>8xp</span> to fully heal the "
"lowest-health adjacent human ally, and increase its\n"
"          attacks, strikes, and damage by its level. <span color='#dd0000' "
"weight='bold'>Next turn, it dies.</span>"
msgstr ""
"Opfert <span color='#00bbe6' style='italic'>8 EP</span>, um eine Einheit auf "
"einem angrenzenden Feld vollständig zu heilen und\n"
"          ihre Angriffe, Zahl der Treffer und Schaden um ihr Level zu "
"erhöhen. Wirkt auf den nächsten menschlichen Verbündeten\n"
"          mit den geringsten LP. <span color='#dd0000' weight='bold'>Die "
"Einheit stirbt in der nächsten Runde.</span>"

#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/lua/skill_set.lua:49
msgid "Animate Mud"
msgstr "Schlamm beleben"

#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/lua/skill_set.lua:51
msgid ""
"Learn to recruit <i><ref dst='unit_Mudcrawler'>Mudcrawlers</ref></i>. "
"Mudcrawlers gain +100% damage and XP\n"
"               while adjacent to you, but dissolve at the end of each "
"scenario."
msgstr ""
"Erlernt die Ausbildung von <i><ref dst='unit_Mudcrawler'>Schlammkriechern</"
"ref></i>. Schlammkriecher erhalten\n"
"               +100% Schaden und EP, wenn sie auf einem Eurer Nachbarfelder "
"stehen. Jedoch zerfallen sie \n"
"               am Ende jedes Szenarios wieder zu Schlamm."

#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/lua/skill_set.lua:63
msgid "Chill Touch"
msgstr "Eiskalte Hand"

#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/lua/skill_set.lua:65
msgid ""
"Melee 6x3 cold, <i><ref dst='weaponspecial_slow'>slows</ref></i>. Replaces "
"your default melee attack."
msgstr ""
"Nahkampf 6x3 Kälte, <i><ref dst='weaponspecial_slow'>verlangsamt</ref></i> "
"den Gegner. Ersetzt den normalen Nahkampfangriff."

#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/lua/skill_set.lua:72
msgid "Levitate"
msgstr "Levitation"

#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/lua/skill_set.lua:74
msgid ""
"Spend <span color='#00bbe6' style='italic'>4 XP</span> to gain <i>flight</i> "
"and the <i><ref dst='ability_skirmisher'>skirmisher</ref></i> ability until "
"the start of your next turn or until cancelled."
msgstr ""
"Opfert <span color='#00bbe6' style='italic'>4 EP</span> um bis zum Beginn "
"Eures nächsten Zuges oder bis zur Aufhebung zu <i>fliegen</i> und die "
"<i><ref dst='ability_skirmisher'>Plänkler</ref></i>-Fertigkeit zu erhalten."

#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/lua/skill_set.lua:82
msgid "Find Familiar"
msgstr "Vertrauten finden"

#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/lua/skill_set.lua:84
msgid ""
"Begin each scenario with your trusty pet <i><ref dst='unit_Raven'>Raven</"
"ref></i>.\n"
"               Your familiar’s level and XP persist across scenarios, but "
"reset if it dies."
msgstr ""
"Beginnt jedes Szenario mit Eurem treuen <i><ref dst='unit_Raven'>Raben</"
"ref></i>.\n"
"               Stufe und EP Eures Vertrauten bleiben in folgenden Szenarien "
"erhalten.\n"
"               Wenn er stirbt, werden sie zurückgesetzt."

#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/lua/skill_set.lua:91
msgid "Mnemonic"
msgstr "Schnellmerker"

#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/lua/skill_set.lua:93
msgid "Whenever an adjacent ally gains XP, you gain the same amount of XP."
msgstr ""
"Immer wenn ein Verbündeter auf einem benachbarten Feld EP erhält, erhaltet "
"Ihr dieselbe Menge an EP."

#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/lua/skill_set.lua:105
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/lua/skill_set.lua:171
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/lua/skill_set.lua:222
msgid "Fireball"
msgstr "Feuerball"

#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/lua/skill_set.lua:107
msgid "Ranged 8x4 fire, <i><ref dst='weaponspecial_magical'>magical</ref></i>."
msgstr ""
"Fernkampf 8x4 Feuer, <i><ref dst='weaponspecial_magical'>Magischer Angriff</"
"ref></i>."

#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/lua/skill_set.lua:114
msgid "Siphon"
msgstr "Anzapfen"

#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/lua/skill_set.lua:116
msgid ""
"Ranged 8x4 arcane, <i><ref dst='weaponspecial_magical'>magical</ref></i> and "
"<i><ref dst='weaponspecial_drains'>drains</ref></i>."
msgstr ""
"Fernkampf 8x4 Arkan, <i><ref dst='weaponspecial_magical'>Magischer Angriff</"
"ref></i>, der <i><ref dst='weaponspecial_drains'>Lebensentzug</ref></i> "
"bewirkt."

#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/lua/skill_set.lua:123
msgid "Blizzard"
msgstr "Schneesturm"

#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/lua/skill_set.lua:125
msgid ""
"Spend <span color='#00bbe6' style='italic'>16 XP</span> and <span "
"color='#c06a61' style='italic'>your attack</span> to <i><ref "
"dst='weaponspecial_slows'>slow</ref></i> enemy units and freeze terrain in a "
"3-hex radius."
msgstr ""
"Opfert <span color='#00bbe6' style='italic'>16 EP</span> und <span "
"color='#c06a61' style='italic'>Euren Angriff</span>, um feindliche \n"
"          Einheiten in einem Radius von 3 Feldern zu <i><ref "
"dst='weaponspecial_slows'>verlangsamen</ref></i> und das Gelände "
"einzufrieren."

#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/lua/skill_set.lua:133
msgid "Counterspell"
msgstr "Gegenzauber"

#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/lua/skill_set.lua:135
msgid ""
"Spend <span color='#00bbe6' style='italic'>16 XP</span> to <i>disallow <ref "
"dst='weaponspecial_magical'>magical</ref> attacks</i> in a 3-hex radius, "
"until cancelled.\n"
"          Disables Delfador’s spells, but not his passive skills."
msgstr ""
"Opfert <span color='#00bbe6' style='italic'>16 EP</span>, um bis zur "
"Aufhebung <i><ref dst='weaponspecial_magical'>magische Angriffe</ref></i> in "
"einem \n"
"          Radius von 3 Feldern zu verhindern. Deaktiviert Delfadors Zauber, "
"aber nicht seine passiven Fertigkeiten."

#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/lua/skill_set.lua:143
msgid "Polymorph"
msgstr "Verwandlung"

#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/lua/skill_set.lua:145
msgid ""
"Transform into a <ref dst='unit_Frost Stoat Poly'>stoat</ref> (<span "
"color='#00bbe6' style='italic'>1 XP</span>), <ref dst='unit_Cave Bear "
"Poly'>bear</ref> (<span color='#00bbe6' style='italic'>8 XP</span>), <ref "
"dst='unit_Giant Crab'>crab</ref> (<span color='#00bbe6' style='italic'>16 "
"XP</span>), or <ref dst='unit_Roc'>roc</ref> (<span color='#00bbe6' "
"style='italic'>32 XP</span>). Lasts until cancelled.\n"
"           Replaces Delfador’s attacks, spells, and passives, but does not "
"affect hitpoints."
msgstr ""
"Verwandelt Euch in ein <ref dst='unit_Frost Stoat Poly'>Schneehermelin</ref> "
"(<span color='#00bbe6' style='italic'>1 EP</span>), einen <ref "
"dst='unit_Cave Bear Poly'>Höhlenbären</ref> (<span color='#00bbe6' "
"style='italic'>8 EP</span>), einen <ref dst='unit_Giant Crab'>Riesenkrebs</"
"ref> (<span color='#00bbe6' style='italic'>16 EP</span>) oder einen <ref "
"dst='unit_Roc'>Roc</ref> (<span color='#00bbe6' style='italic'>32 EP</"
"span>). Hält bis zur Aufhebung an.\n"
"           Ersetzt Delfadors Angriffe, Zauber und passiven Fähigkeiten, "
"beeinflusst aber seine Lebenspunkte nicht."

#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/lua/skill_set.lua:157
msgid "Glamour"
msgstr "Glamour"

#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/lua/skill_set.lua:159
msgid "Gain the <i><ref dst='ability_leadership'>leadership</ref></i> ability."
msgstr ""
"Erhaltet die Fertigkeit <i><ref dst='ability_leadership'>Führungsqualitäten</"
"ref></i>."

#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/lua/skill_set.lua:173
msgid ""
"Ranged 12x4 fire, <i><ref dst='weaponspecial_magical'>magical</ref></i>."
msgstr ""
"Fernkampf 12x4 Feuer, <i><ref dst='weaponspecial_magical'>Magischer Angriff</"
"ref></i>."

#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/lua/skill_set.lua:180
msgid "Dancing Daggers"
msgstr "Tanzende Dolche"

#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/lua/skill_set.lua:182
msgid ""
"Ranged 5x8 blade, <i><ref dst='weaponspecial_backstab'>backstab</ref></i>"
msgstr ""
"Fernkampf 5x8 Klinge, <i><ref dst='weaponspecial_backstab'>Hinterlistiger "
"Angriff</ref></i>"

#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/lua/skill_set.lua:189
msgid "Enthrall"
msgstr "Bann"

#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/lua/skill_set.lua:191
msgid ""
"Spend <span color='#00bbe6' style='italic'>48 XP</span> and <span "
"color='#c06a61' style='italic'>your attack</span> to magically disguise "
"yourself as an awe-inspiring drake.\n"
"          Enemies in a 2-hex radius suffer a -10% penalty to both their "
"terrain defense\n"
"          (chance to evade) and chance to hit (except for magical attacks). "
"Lasts until cancelled."
msgstr ""
"Opfert <span color='#00bbe6' style='italic'>48 EP</span> und <span "
"color='#c06a61' style='italic'>Euren Angriff</span>, um Euch magisch als "
"furchteinflößender Drake zu tarnen.\n"
"          Feinde in einem Radius von 2 Feldern erleiden einen Malus von -10 "
"% sowohl auf ihre Geländeverteidigung\n"
"          (Ausweichchance) als auch ihre Trefferchance (außer gegen magische "
"Angriffe). Hält bis zur Aufhebung an."

#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/lua/skill_set.lua:199
msgid "Animate Fire"
msgstr "Feuer beleben"

#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/lua/skill_set.lua:201
msgid ""
"Learn to recruit <i><ref dst='unit_Fire Guardian'>Fire Guardians</ref></i>. "
"Fire Guardians gain +100% damage and XP\n"
"               while adjacent to you, but dissipate at the end of each "
"scenario."
msgstr ""
"Erlernt die Ausbildung von <i><ref dst='unit_Fire Guardian'>Feuerwächtern</"
"ref></i>. Feuerwächter erhalten +100 % Schaden und EP\n"
"               solange sie auf einem Eurer Nachbarfelder stehen, zerfallen "
"aber am Ende jedes Szenarios."

#. [floating_text]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/lua/skill_set.lua:208
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/00_Graduation.cfg:475
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/utils/spellcasting.cfg:1796
msgid "Contingency"
msgstr "Lebensversicherung"

#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/lua/skill_set.lua:210
msgid ""
"Whenever one of your human soldiers dies, they are instead returned safely "
"to your recall list."
msgstr ""
"Immer wenn einer Eurer menschlichen Kameraden sterben würde, kehrt er "
"stattdessen auf Eure Einberufungsliste zurück."

#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/lua/skill_set.lua:224
msgid ""
"Ranged 17x4 fire, <i><ref dst='weaponspecial_magical'>magical</ref></i>."
msgstr ""
"Fernkampf 17x4 Feuer, <i><ref dst='weaponspecial_magical'>Magischer Angriff</"
"ref></i>."

#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/lua/skill_set.lua:231
msgid "Chain Lightning"
msgstr "Kettenblitz"

#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/lua/skill_set.lua:233
msgid ""
"Ranged 14x3 fire, <i><ref dst='weaponspecial_magical'>magical</ref></i>. "
"This attack can be used multiple times on offense, but\n"
"              consecutive uses strike one fewer time."
msgstr ""
"Fernkampf 14x3 Feuer, <i><ref dst='weaponspecial_magical'>Magischer Angriff</"
"ref></i>. Der Angriff kann mehrmals offensiv eingesetzt\n"
"              werden; bei mehrfacher Nutzung reduziert sich die Anzahl der "
"Schläge."

#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/lua/skill_set.lua:240
msgid "Time Dilation"
msgstr "Zeitverzerrung"

#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/lua/skill_set.lua:242
msgid ""
"Spend <span color='#00bbe6' style='italic'>48 XP</span> to grant yourself "
"and all allies double movement and a second attack this turn.\n"
"          When this turn ends, affected units become <ref "
"dst='weaponspecial_slows'>slowed</ref>."
msgstr ""
"Opfert <span color='#00bbe6' style='italic'>48 EP</span>, um Euch und allen "
"Verbündeten in dieser Runde doppelte Bewegungsrate und\n"
"          einen zweiten Angriff zu gewähren. Wenn die Runde endet, werden "
"die betroffenen Einheiten <ref dst='weaponspecial_slows'>verlangsamt</ref>."

#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/lua/skill_set.lua:250
msgid "Cataclysm"
msgstr "Kataklysmus"

#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/lua/skill_set.lua:252
msgid ""
"Spend <span color='#00bbe6' style='italic'>99 XP</span> and <span "
"color='#c06a61' style='italic'>your attack</span> to blast everything in a 5-"
"hex radius. Units (except Delfador) will be reduced\n"
"          to 1 HP. Dries water, melts snow, burns forest, and levels castles/"
"villages."
msgstr ""
"Opfert <span color='#00bbe6' style='italic'>99 EP</span> und <span "
"color='#c06a61' style='italic'>Euren Angriff</span>, um alles in 5 Feldern "
"Umkreis zu vernichten.\n"
"          Alle Einheiten (außer Delfador) werden auf 1 LP reduziert. "
"Trocknet Wasserfelder aus, schmilzt Schnee, verbrennt Wälder und zerstört "
"Burgen und Dörfer."

#. [lua]: display_skills_dialog
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/lua/spellcasting.lua:49
msgid "Cast Delfador’s Spells"
msgstr "Delfadors Zauber wirken"

#. [lua]: display_skills_dialog
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/lua/spellcasting.lua:49
msgid "Select Delfador’s Spells"
msgstr "Delfadors Zauber auswählen"

#. [lua]: display_skills_dialog
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/lua/spellcasting.lua:50
msgid "Cast the Apprentice’s Spells"
msgstr "Zauber des Lehrlings wirken"

#. [lua]: display_skills_dialog
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/lua/spellcasting.lua:50
msgid "Select the Apprentice’s Spells"
msgstr "Zauber des Lehrlings auswählen"

#. [lua]: display_skills_dialog
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/lua/spellcasting.lua:56
msgid ""
"<span size='small'><i>Delfador knows many useful spells, and will learn more "
"as he levels-up automatically throughout the campaign. Delfador does not use "
"XP to level-up. Instead,\n"
"Delfador uses XP to cast certain spells. If you select spells that cost XP, "
"<b>double- or right-click on Delfador to cast them</b>. You can only cast 1 "
"spell per turn.</i></span>"
msgstr ""
"<span size='small'><i>Delfador kennt viele nützliche Zauber und lernt im "
"Laufe der Kampagne automatisch weitere, wenn er aufsteigt. Delfador "
"verwendet EP\n"
"nicht zum Aufstieg. Stattdessen verwendet Delfador EP, um bestimmte Zauber "
"zu wirken. Zauber, die EP kosten, könnt Ihr wirken, indem Ihr\n"
"<b>auf Delfador doppelklickt oder mit der rechten Maustaste klickt</b>. Ihr "
"könnt pro Runde nur 1 Zauber wirken.</i></span>"

#. [lua]: display_skills_dialog
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/lua/spellcasting.lua:57
msgid ""
"<span size='small'><i>The apprentice knows several useful spells, and will "
"learn more as he levels-up automatically throughout the campaign. The "
"apprentice does not use XP to level-up. Instead,\n"
"he uses XP to cast certain spells. If you select spells that cost XP,"
"<b>double- or right-click on the apprentice to cast them</b>. You can only "
"cast 1 spell per turn.</i></span>"
msgstr ""
"<span size='small'><i>Der Lehrling kennt mehrere nützliche Zauber und lernt "
"im Laufe der Kampagne automatisch weitere, wenn er aufsteigt. Der Lehrling "
"verwendet EP\n"
"nicht zum Aufstieg. Stattdessen verwendet er EP, um bestimmte Zauber zu "
"wirken. Zauber, die EP kosten, könnt Ihr wirken, indem ihr\n"
"<b>auf den Lehrling doppelklickt oder mit der rechten Maustaste klickt</b>. "
"Ihr könnt pro Runde nur 1 Zauber wirken.</i></span>"

#. [lua]: display_skills_dialog
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/lua/spellcasting.lua:131
msgid "Confirm Spells <small><i>(can be changed every scenario)</i></small>"
msgstr ""
"Zauber bestätigen <small><i>(kann in jedem Szenario geändert werden)</i></"
"small>"

#. [lua]: display_skills_dialog
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/lua/spellcasting.lua:134
msgid "Choose Later"
msgstr "Später wählen"

#. [lua]: wesnoth.interface.game_display.unit_status
#. [chance_to_hit]: id=skill_illusion
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/lua/theme.lua:13
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/utils/spellcasting.cfg:1464
msgid ""
"dazed: This unit is dazed. It suffers a -10% penalty to both its defense and "
"chance to hit (except for magical attacks)."
msgstr ""
"Benommen: Diese Einheit ist benommen. Sie erleidet einen Malus von -10 % "
"sowohl auf ihre Verteidigung als auch auf ihre Trefferchance (außer gegen "
"magische Angriffe)."

#. [scenario]: id=00_Graduation
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/00_Graduation.cfg:6
msgid "Graduation"
msgstr "Abschlussprüfung"

#. [leader]: type=Delfador L1
#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/00_Graduation.cfg:20
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/00_Graduation.cfg:208
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/00_Graduation.cfg:210
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/00_Graduation.cfg:213
msgid "Apprentice"
msgstr "Lehrling"

#. [side]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/00_Graduation.cfg:26
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/00_Graduation.cfg:34
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/01_Stirrings_of_War.cfg:59
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/02_Fort_Garard.cfg:25
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/03_The_Ambassador.cfg:33
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:41
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/05_The_Deceiver.cfg:39
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/06_Ring_of_Swords.cfg:30
msgid "Isle of Alduin"
msgstr "Insel Alduin"

#. [side]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/00_Graduation.cfg:41
msgid "Summoned Monsters"
msgstr "Herbeigerufene Monster"

#. [message]
#. an informational plaque on a statue of a female arch-mage
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/00_Graduation.cfg:84
msgid ""
"<i>In honor of master Heryera, who gave her life in defense of Elensefar "
"against the lich Ras-Tabahn.</i>"
msgstr ""
"<i>Zu Ehren von Meisterin Heryera, die ihr Leben für die Verteidigung von "
"Elensefar gegen den Lich Ras-Tabahn gab.</i>"

#. [unit]: id=Leollyn
#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/00_Graduation.cfg:182
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/00_Graduation.cfg:249
msgid "Leollyn"
msgstr "Leollyn"

#. [unit]: id=Saegwylyn, gender=female
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/00_Graduation.cfg:200
msgid "Saegwylyn"
msgstr "Saegwylyn"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/00_Graduation.cfg:234
msgid "The Author"
msgstr "Der Autor"

#. [message]
#. notice that appears at the beginning of the scenario if you select Deadly difficulty
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/00_Graduation.cfg:239
msgid ""
"NOTE: ‘Deadly’ difficulty is intended to be a frighteningly difficult "
"challenge even for experienced players! If you’re new to Wesnoth, I strongly "
"suggest trying a lower difficulty."
msgstr ""
"HINWEIS: Der Schwierigkeitsgrad »Tödlich« ist als furchteinflößend schwere "
"Herausforderung selbst für erfahrene Spieler gedacht! Wenn Ihr neu bei "
"Wesnoth seid, empfehle ich Euch dringend, einen niedrigeren "
"Schwierigkeitsgrad zu probieren."

#. [message]
#. notice that appears at the beginning of the scenario if you select Hard difficulty
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/00_Graduation.cfg:246
msgid ""
"NOTE: ‘Hard’ difficulty is intended to be a serious challenge even for "
"experienced players! If you’re new to Wesnoth, you may want to try a lower "
"difficulty."
msgstr ""
"HINWEIS: Der Schwierigkeitsgrad »Schwer« ist als ernsthafte Herausforderung "
"selbst für erfahrene Spieler gedacht! Wenn Ihr neu bei Wesnoth seid, solltet "
"Ihr vielleicht einen niedrigeren Schwierigkeitsgrad ausprobieren."

#. [message]: speaker=Methor
#. the fire wraiths are not visible yet. Delfador is about to appear on the left edge of the map
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/00_Graduation.cfg:255
msgid "Faster, faster! The wraiths will soon be upon you!"
msgstr "Schneller, schneller! Die Geisterwesen werden Euch bald erreichen!"

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#. referencing events that happened minutes before the beginning of the campaign
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/00_Graduation.cfg:270
msgid ""
"Hey, how was I supposed to know the halfway cave was warded! All I did was "
"throw a few celebratory firebolts! For the spectators, you know?"
msgstr ""
"Hey, woher sollte ich wissen, dass die Höhle in der Mitte geschützt war! Ich "
"habe nur ein paar feierliche Feuerpfeile geworfen! Für die Zuschauer, "
"versteht Ihr?"

#. [message]: speaker=Methor
#. there's a blue orb at the east edge of the map, which will dispel the fire guardians that will soon appear to chase Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/00_Graduation.cfg:275
msgid "Just hurry and get to the dispel orb!"
msgstr "Beeilt Euch einfach damit, die Bannkugel zu erreichen!"

#. [objective]: condition=win
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/00_Graduation.cfg:283
msgid "Reach the blue orb at the east edge of the map"
msgstr "Erreicht die blaue Kugel am Ostrand der Karte"

#. [objective]: condition=lose
#. Delfador is currently just named "apprentice". He doesn't get his name until scenario 2
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/00_Graduation.cfg:288
msgid "Death of the Apprentice"
msgstr "Tod des Lehrlings"

#. [message]: speaker=Methor
#. this tells the player that 1) Delfador is Methor's apprentice, and 2) Delfador is very reckless
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/00_Graduation.cfg:306
msgid ""
"Out of all the masters in Alduin, why did the sages curse me with the most "
"reckless apprentice in all Wesnoth?"
msgstr ""
"Warum musste von allen Meistern in Alduin ausgerechnet ich derjenige sein, "
"dem die Weisen den leichtsinnigsten Lehrling in ganz Wesnoth zuwiesen?"

#. [message]: speaker=Methor
#. this line is spoken as soon as the fire guardians enter the map
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/00_Graduation.cfg:324
msgid "The wraiths are catching up! Keep moving!"
msgstr "Die Geisterwesen holen auf! Weiter!"

#. [message]: speaker=Saegwylyn
#. another of Delfador's instructors; implying Delfador has attempted to firebolt the fire guardians before, and it ended badly
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/00_Graduation.cfg:329
msgid "10 copper says he tries to firebolt them again..."
msgstr ""
"10 Kupfer darauf, dass er sie gleich wieder mit Feuerpfeilen beschießt…"

#. [message]: speaker=Methor
#. Levitate is one of many spells that Delfador will have access to throughout this scenario. It grants him flight and skirmisher, which
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/00_Graduation.cfg:334
msgid ""
"Ignore her. You’re making good time so far — now cast Levitate and slip past "
"the eyestalks! You may need to cast it several turns in a row to keep ahead "
"of the wraiths."
msgstr ""
"Ignoriert sie. Ihr seid bisher gut in der Zeit – nun wirkt Levitation und "
"schlüpft an den Stielaugen vorbei! Ihr müsst ihn vielleicht mehrere Runden "
"hintereinander wirken, damit die Geister Euch nicht erwischen."

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/00_Graduation.cfg:338
msgid "Levitate? Master, are you sure?"
msgstr "Levitation? Meister, seid Ihr sicher?"

#. [message]: speaker=Methor
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/00_Graduation.cfg:342
msgid ""
"Oh for the love of— remember what happened last time you tried to fight? "
"Just do it!"
msgstr ""
"Um Himmels willen – habt Ihr schon vergessen, was beim letzten Mal geschah, "
"als Ihr kämpfen wolltet? Tut es einfach!"

#. [object]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/00_Graduation.cfg:347
msgid "Casting Spells:"
msgstr "Zauber wirken:"

#. [object]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/00_Graduation.cfg:348
msgid "Double- or right-click on the apprentice to cast spells."
msgstr ""
"Doppelklickt oder klickt mit der rechten Maustaste auf den Lehrling, um "
"Zauber zu wirken."

#. [message]: speaker=Methor
#. spoken after Delfador attacks the fire guardians, referencing the "10 copper" bet from earlier. Since there are 3 guardians and they have 50% fire resistance, this is not a wise move by Delfador.
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/00_Graduation.cfg:365
msgid "All right, all right! It’s just as you said."
msgstr "Na schön, na schön! Ihr hattet recht."

#. [message]: speaker=Saegwylyn
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/00_Graduation.cfg:370
msgid "10 more copper for me!"
msgstr "Das sind 10 Kupfer für mich!"

#. [message]: speaker=Saegwylyn
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/00_Graduation.cfg:383
msgid ""
"So he does know proper magic after all. It only took four failed exams..."
msgstr ""
"Also beherrscht er doch richtige Magie. Es hat ja auch nur vier misslungene "
"Prüfungen gebraucht…"

#. [message]: speaker=Methor
#. if the levitate spell ends over impassable terrain (like lava), Delfador dies
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/00_Graduation.cfg:397
msgid ""
"Almost there! Just fly across the chasm and touch the orb — and make sure "
"your levitate spell doesn’t end over lava!"
msgstr ""
"Fast geschafft! Fliegt einfach über den Abgrund und berührt die Kugel – und "
"passt auf, dass Euer Levitationszauber nicht über der Lava verlischt!"

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/00_Graduation.cfg:411
msgid "Hello, my adoring fans!"
msgstr "Hallo, meine begeisterten Fans!"

#. [message]: speaker=Mirya
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/00_Graduation.cfg:415
msgid "Hey, what’re you doing! This isn’t the normal route!"
msgstr "He, was macht Ihr da! Das ist nicht der normale Weg!"

#. [message]: speaker=Rolyn
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/00_Graduation.cfg:419
msgid "We’d better get out of here. Remember what happened on his last exam?"
msgstr ""
"Wir verschwinden besser von hier. Wisst ihr noch, was bei seiner letzten "
"Prüfung passiert ist?"

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#. Delfador has just reached the end of the obstacle course / final exam (and the end of the scenario0
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/00_Graduation.cfg:539
msgid "Yes! I’ve made it! This time has to be good enough."
msgstr "Ja! Ich habe es geschafft! Diesmal muss es gut genug sein."

#. [message]: speaker=Leollyn
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/00_Graduation.cfg:544
msgid "Well, what do you think?"
msgstr "Nun, was meint Ihr?"

#. [message]: speaker=Saegwylyn
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/00_Graduation.cfg:550
msgid ""
"I say no. A mage needs wisdom; this apprentice cares only for his own "
"amusement. This one is a petty magician, not a wise sage or advisor of kings."
msgstr ""
"Ich sage nein. Ein Magier braucht Weisheit; dieser Lehrling kümmert sich nur "
"um sein eigenes Vergnügen. Das ist ein armseliger Jahrmarktsgaukler, kein "
"weiser Gelehrter oder Ratgeber von Königen."

#. [message]: speaker=Methor
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/00_Graduation.cfg:554
msgid ""
"I say yes. I admit my apprentice enjoys the spotlight more than most, but "
"with this much magical aptitude who wouldn’t want to show off?"
msgstr ""
"Ich sage ja. Ich gebe zu, mein Lehrling sonnt sich mehr als die meisten im "
"Rampenlicht, aber bei so viel magischem Talent kann man ein wenig Angeberei "
"doch verstehen?"

#. [message]: speaker=Methor
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/00_Graduation.cfg:558
msgid ""
"I think it’s obvious this is one of the most gifted magi we’ve trained in "
"years. The skill is innate; the wisdom will come with time."
msgstr ""
"Ich denke, es liegt auf der Hand, dass er einer der begabtesten Magier ist, "
"den wir in den letzten Jahren ausgebildet haben. Das Talent ist angeboren; "
"die Weisheit kommt mit der Zeit."

#. [message]: speaker=Leollyn
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/00_Graduation.cfg:563
msgid "So mine is the deciding vote. Very well, I’ve made up my mind."
msgstr ""
"Also liegt die entscheidende Stimme bei mir. Wohlan, ich habe mich "
"entschieden."

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#. non sequitur. The screen has faded to black, and Delfador is hearing a voice with no apparent origin. In scenario 4, this is later revealed to be the elvish seer Elende, prophesying about Delfador's future.
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/00_Graduation.cfg:590
msgid ""
"<i>The Deceiver weaves the twine encircling the puppets in the court of "
"royals.</i>"
msgstr ""
"<i>Die Spinne webt die Fäden, die die Puppen am Hof der Könige führen.</i>"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/00_Graduation.cfg:594
msgid ""
"<i>Fatherless prince and sovereignless king, the balance of man hangs upon "
"this thread.</i>"
msgstr ""
"<i>Vaterloser Prinz und machtloser König, das Gleichgewicht der Menschen "
"hängt an diesem Faden.</i>"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/00_Graduation.cfg:598
msgid ""
"<i>Should force and fire brandish themselves where wisdom and pity are left "
"wanting, this string of fate shall inexorably be sundered.</i>"
msgstr ""
"<i>Wenn Gewalt und Feuer walten, wo Weisheit und Mitleid fehlen, so wird "
"dieser Faden des Schicksals unweigerlich zerreißen.</i>"

#. [message]: speaker=Leollyn
#. the screen has faded back to normal, and master Leollyn is annoyed that Delfador wasn't paying attention
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/00_Graduation.cfg:611
msgid "Apprentice! Are you listening? I’m trying to congratulate you!"
msgstr ""
"Herr Lehrling! Hört Ihr mir überhaupt zu? Ich versuche, Euch zu gratulieren!"

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/00_Graduation.cfg:615
msgid "But who— what— um, yes, I must have drifted off."
msgstr "Aber wer… was… äh, ja, ich muss wohl weggedriftet sein."

#. [message]: speaker=Leollyn
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/00_Graduation.cfg:619
msgid ""
"...as I was saying... apprentice, congratulations on your successful "
"completion of the practical portion of your graduation exam! Now we proceed "
"to the written section; please conjure your quill and parchment..."
msgstr ""
"…wie ich sagte… Lehrling, Glückwunsch zum erfolgreichen Abschluss des "
"praktischen Teils Eurer Abschlussprüfung! Wir fahren mit dem schriftlichen "
"Teil fort; beschwört bitte Euer Schreibrohr und Pergament…"

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#. Delfador has just taken lethal damage
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/00_Graduation.cfg:639
msgid "Oh no! Master, help!"
msgstr "Nein! Meister, helft mir!"

#. [message]: speaker=Methor
#. Methor casts a spell to save Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/00_Graduation.cfg:644
msgid "I’ll save you!"
msgstr "Ich rette Euch!"

#. [message]: speaker=Methor
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/00_Graduation.cfg:659
msgid ""
"(sigh) Not again! I suppose you’ll have to retry the exam next year... for "
"the sixth time."
msgstr ""
"(seufz) Nicht schon wieder! Das bedeutet wohl, dass Ihr die Prüfung nächstes "
"Jahr erneut versuchen müsst… zum sechsten Mal."

#. [scenario]: id=01_Stirrings_of_War
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/01_Stirrings_of_War.cfg:10
msgid "Stirrings of War"
msgstr "Rauch am Horizont"

#. [part]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/01_Stirrings_of_War.cfg:28
msgid ""
"In the year 481 after the founding of Wesnoth, King Garard the Second grew "
"discontent."
msgstr ""
"Im Jahr 481 nach der Gründung Wesnoths begann König Garard der Zweite, "
"unzufrieden zu werden."

#. [part]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/01_Stirrings_of_War.cfg:31
msgid ""
"With the Estmarks secured and the southern bandits pacified, his empire had "
"grown large and powerful. Garard’s marriage to the young Asheviere had "
"secured him a queen, as well as the promise of an heir. Yet despite these "
"achievements, the restless king could find no peace."
msgstr ""
"Nachdem die Ostmarken gesichert und die Banditen im Süden befriedet waren, "
"war sein Reich groß und mächtig geworden. Garards Vermählung mit der jungen "
"Asheviere hatte ihm eine Königin sowie die Aussicht auf einen Erben "
"gesichert. Doch trotz all dieser Errungenschaften war der tatendurstige "
"König nicht zufrieden."

#. [part]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/01_Stirrings_of_War.cfg:35
msgid ""
"The king’s love lay in sword and shield, in battle and blood. Dissatisfied "
"with a life of languor among the estates of Weldyn, Garard looked instead to "
"the orcs of the Heart Mountains, whose raids had long been a nuisance across "
"his northern border."
msgstr ""
"Des Königs Liebe galt Schwert und Schild, Schlacht und Blut. Gelangweilt vom "
"trägen Alltag bei der Verwaltung von Weldyns Gütern, wandte Garard sich "
"stattdessen den Orks der Herzberge zu, deren Überfälle seit langem ein "
"Ärgernis an seiner Nordgrenze waren."

#. [part]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/01_Stirrings_of_War.cfg:39
msgid ""
"Eager to retaliate, the king sent messengers far and wide. He called to arms "
"an expeditionary force to cross the Great River and lay claim to orcish "
"lands; a great show of power to secure Wesnoth’s might."
msgstr ""
"Begierig auf Vergeltung sandte der König Boten in alle Himmelsrichtungen. Er "
"rief ein Expeditionsheer zu den Waffen, das den Großen Fluss überqueren und "
"orkische Lande beanspruchen sollte; eine gewaltige Demonstration der Stärke, "
"um Wesnoths Macht zu festigen."

#. [part]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/01_Stirrings_of_War.cfg:43
msgid ""
"One of these messengers rode to the venerable Academy of Magic on Alduin, "
"summoning a contingent of magi to support Garard’s endeavor. A particular "
"young apprentice was especially enthusiastic..."
msgstr ""
"Einer dieser Boten erreichte auch die ehrwürdige Akademie der Magie auf "
"Alduin und stellte ein Kontingent von Magiern auf, um Garards Vorhaben zu "
"unterstützen. Ein gewisser junger Lehrling war Feuer und Flamme…"

#. [side]: type=Orcish Grunt, id=Ozgob
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/01_Stirrings_of_War.cfg:70
msgid "Ozgob"
msgstr "Ozgob"

#. [side]: type=Orcish Grunt, id=Ozgob
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/01_Stirrings_of_War.cfg:78
msgid "Clan Whitefang"
msgstr "Reißzahn-Clan"

#. [side]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/01_Stirrings_of_War.cfg:135
msgid "Weldyn"
msgstr "Weldyn"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/01_Stirrings_of_War.cfg:156
msgid "15 gold"
msgstr "15 Gold"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/01_Stirrings_of_War.cfg:156
msgid "Treasure! Looks like a previous victim of the goblins."
msgstr "Beute! Sieht aus wie ein früheres Opfer der Goblins."

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/01_Stirrings_of_War.cfg:193
msgid "Are we there yet?"
msgstr "Sind wir schon da?"

#. [message]: speaker=Methor
#. a "seeker spell" is a made-up word to describe some kind of spell that helps you find your way to a destination
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/01_Stirrings_of_War.cfg:198
msgid ""
"Nearer than the last time you asked, yet further than we will be the next. "
"Really apprentice, would it kill you to learn a proper seeker spell?"
msgstr ""
"Näher als beim letzten Mal, als Ihr gefragt habt, und doch weiter als beim "
"nächsten. Im Ernst, Lehrling, würde es Euch etwas ausmachen, einen "
"ordentlichen Suchzauber zu lernen?"

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#. Delfador has never met King Garard II, but rather idolizes him
#. "no need to be so glum" is echoed by Methor in S13x
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/01_Stirrings_of_War.cfg:204
msgid ""
"There’s no need to be so glum, master. As the head of our delegation, you’ll "
"even get to counsel with the king himself! What I wouldn’t give for a chance "
"to prove myself to him..."
msgstr ""
"Es gibt keinen Grund, so trübselig zu sein, Meister. Als Anführer unserer "
"Gesandtschaft werdet Ihr sogar den König persönlich beraten dürfen! Was gäbe "
"ich dafür, mich ihm beweisen zu können…"

#. [message]: speaker=Methor
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/01_Stirrings_of_War.cfg:208
msgid "Do you hear that?"
msgstr "Hört Ihr das?"

#. [message]: speaker=Methor
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/01_Stirrings_of_War.cfg:208
msgid "Quiet!"
msgstr "Still!"

#. [message]: speaker=Ozgob
#. 'stragglers' refers to soldiers (like Delfador and Methor) who are joining Garard's war-camp, but are arriving late
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/01_Stirrings_of_War.cfg:218
msgid ""
"“Kill the stragglers”, they says. “You’ll have our best warriors”, they "
"says. N’ all I get are a bunch o’ lousy goblins? Lousy lazy lying—"
msgstr ""
"»Tötet die Nachzügler«, sagten sie. »Ihr kriegt unsere besten Krieger«, "
"sagten sie. Und was bekomme ich? Einen Haufen lausiger Goblins? Lausige, "
"faule, verlogene…"

#. [message]: role=gobbo1
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/01_Stirrings_of_War.cfg:223
msgid "They’re here, they’re here! Humans on the clan road!"
msgstr "Sie sind da, sie sind da! Menschen auf dem Clanweg!"

#. [message]: speaker=Ozgob
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/01_Stirrings_of_War.cfg:227
msgid ""
"—then grab your spear, you loathsome lout! Don’t let them link up with the "
"rest of their army!"
msgstr ""
"…dann greif zu deinem Speer, du widerlicher Tölpel! Bevor sie sich mit dem "
"Rest ihres Heeres vereinen!"

#. [message]: role=gobbo1
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/01_Stirrings_of_War.cfg:231
msgid "No, no, no! No fight! I run away!"
msgstr "Nein, nein, nein! Kein Kampf! Ich laufe weg!"

#. [message]: speaker=Ozgob
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/01_Stirrings_of_War.cfg:238
msgid "Why you runtish, yellow—"
msgstr "Du feiger, elender…"

#. [message]
#. multiple goblins are running away
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/01_Stirrings_of_War.cfg:245
msgid "Wait for me!"
msgstr "Wartet auf mich!"

#. [message]: role=gobbo3
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/01_Stirrings_of_War.cfg:249
msgid "Run away! Back to the swamp!"
msgstr "Lauft weg! Zurück zum Sumpf!"

#. [message]: speaker=Ozgob
#. Ozgob has just killed one of the fleeing goblins
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/01_Stirrings_of_War.cfg:257
msgid "I said FORM RANKS! Rousers, get these runts organized!"
msgstr ""
"Ich sagte, GESCHLOSSENE REIHEN! Einpeitscher, bringt diese Rotznasen in Reih "
"und Glied!"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/01_Stirrings_of_War.cfg:261
msgid "Gumpnug"
msgstr "Gumpnug"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/01_Stirrings_of_War.cfg:276
msgid "Bork"
msgstr "Bork"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/01_Stirrings_of_War.cfg:292
msgid "Mirnik"
msgstr "Mirnik"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/01_Stirrings_of_War.cfg:308
msgid "Gump"
msgstr "Gump"

#. [objective]: condition=win
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/01_Stirrings_of_War.cfg:328
msgid "Defeat Ozgob"
msgstr "Besiegt Ozgob"

#. [objective]: condition=lose
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/01_Stirrings_of_War.cfg:332
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/02_Fort_Garard.cfg:418
msgid "Death of Methor or the Apprentice"
msgstr "Methor oder der Lehrling fallen in der Schlacht"

#. [note]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/01_Stirrings_of_War.cfg:340
msgid "Defeat a Goblin Rouser to rout their entourage."
msgstr ""
"Besiegt einen Goblin-Einpeitscher, um seine Begleiter in die Flucht zu "
"schlagen."

#. [object]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/01_Stirrings_of_War.cfg:353
msgid "Choosing Spells:"
msgstr "Zauber auswählen:"

#. [object]
#. Delfador does not yet have a true name; he's only called "apprentice"
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/01_Stirrings_of_War.cfg:355
msgid ""
"Before each scenario in this campaign, you will have the opportunity to "
"select which spells to equip for the upcoming battle. Remember, double- or "
"right-click on the apprentice to cast chosen spells!"
msgstr ""
"Vor jedem Szenario dieser Kampagne habt Ihr die Möglichkeit, die Zauber "
"auszuwählen, die Ihr für die kommende Schlacht verwenden wollt. Erinnert "
"Euch, Ihr könnt den Lehrling doppelt anklicken oder mit der rechten "
"Maustaste auf ihn klicken, um einen Zauber zu wirken!"

#. [message]: speaker=Methor
#. Methor says this when Delfador stands on their keep. Delfador can only recruit mudcrawlers; Methor recruits mages
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/01_Stirrings_of_War.cfg:378
msgid ""
"You’re not yet a journeyman, apprentice! Your mudcrawlers are not without "
"use, but to recruit mages I’ll need to stand on our keep."
msgstr ""
"Ihr seid noch kein Geselle, Lehrling! Eure Schlammkriecher sind nicht ohne "
"Nutzen, aber um richtige Magier auszubilden, muss ich auf unserem Burgfried "
"stehen."

#. [message]: speaker=Methor
#. Methor says this when Delfador stands on their keep. Delfador can not recruit; Methor recruits mages
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/01_Stirrings_of_War.cfg:385
msgid ""
"You’re not yet a journeyman, apprentice! To recruit mages I’ll need to stand "
"on our keep."
msgstr ""
"Ihr seid noch kein Geselle, Lehrling! Um Magier auszubilden, muss ich auf "
"unserem Burgfried stehen."

#. [object]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/01_Stirrings_of_War.cfg:397
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/08_Ruins_of_Saurgrath.cfg:544
msgid "New Recruit:"
msgstr "Neuer Rekrut:"

#. [object]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/01_Stirrings_of_War.cfg:398
msgid ""
"The apprentice is the main character of this campaign, but right now he’s "
"not your leader. Methor is your leader, and he can recruit Mages."
msgstr ""
"Der Lehrling ist die Hauptfigur dieser Kampagne, aber im Moment ist er nicht "
"Euer Anführer. Methor ist Euer Anführer, und er kann Magier ausbilden."

#. [object]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/01_Stirrings_of_War.cfg:400
msgid ""
"Mages are deadly ranged attackers, with accurate <i>magical</i> attacks that "
"are difficult to evade. They have few hitpoints and are highly vulnerable in "
"melee combat, so take good care of them!"
msgstr ""
"Magier sind tödliche Fernkämpfer mit präzisen <i>magischen</i> Angriffen, "
"denen man nur schwer ausweichen kann. Sie haben nicht viele Lebenspunkte und "
"sind im Nahkampf sehr verwundbar, also passt gut auf sie auf!"

#. [message]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/01_Stirrings_of_War.cfg:413
msgid ""
"<i>Rain is purely visual, and has no impact on gameplay. If rain is "
"distracting or reduces performance, you can disable it by opening the "
"Preferences menu (Ctrl-P), selecting “Display”, and unchecking “Animate "
"Map.”</i>"
msgstr ""
"<i>Regen ist nur ein optischer Effekt und hat keinen Einfluss auf das Spiel. "
"Wenn der Regen Euch stört oder die Leistung verringert, könnt Ihr ihn "
"deaktivieren, indem Ihr das Einstellungsmenü (Strg-P) öffnet, »Anzeige« "
"auswählt und »Karte animieren« deaktiviert.</i>"

#. [scenario]: id=01_Stirrings_of_War
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/01_Stirrings_of_War.cfg:502
msgid "Run for your lives!"
msgstr "Rette sich, wer kann!"

#. [scenario]: id=01_Stirrings_of_War
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/01_Stirrings_of_War.cfg:503
msgid "Run! Flee back to the swamp!"
msgstr "Lauft! Flieht zurück in den Sumpf!"

#. [scenario]: id=01_Stirrings_of_War
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/01_Stirrings_of_War.cfg:504
msgid "Noooo, $unit.name!"
msgstr "Neeeein, $unit.name!"

#. [scenario]: id=01_Stirrings_of_War
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/01_Stirrings_of_War.cfg:505
msgid "Flee, flee! $unit.name’s dead!"
msgstr "Flieht, flieht! $unit.name ist tot!"

#. [message]: speaker=Ozgob
#. said in response to goblins running away from the fight
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/01_Stirrings_of_War.cfg:512
msgid "Cowards!! Fight and die like real orcish warriors!"
msgstr "Feiglinge!! Kämpft und sterbt wie echte Orkkrieger!"

#. [message]: speaker=Methor
#. said after any living unit dies (both human and goblin)
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/01_Stirrings_of_War.cfg:538
msgid ""
"(sigh) More casualties of pointless politics. I joined the order to do some "
"<i><b>good</b></i> in the world..."
msgstr ""
"(seufz) Noch mehr Opfer sinnloser Politik. Dabei bin ich dem Orden "
"beigetreten, um in der Welt etwas <i><b>Gutes</b></i> zu tun…"

#. [message]: speaker=Ozgob
#. Ozgob has lost most of his goblins ('runts'), and is about to charge at Delfador personally
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/01_Stirrings_of_War.cfg:551
msgid ""
"I’ve had it with this! Never send a runt to do a warrior’s job. I’ll bring "
"you down myself!"
msgstr ""
"Ich habe die Nase voll davon! Sende keinen Wicht aus, um die Arbeit eines "
"Kriegers zu erledigen. Ich werde Euch selbst zu Fall bringen!"

#. [message]: speaker=Methor
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/01_Stirrings_of_War.cfg:588
msgid ""
"We’ve accumulated a great deal of gold, apprentice. While my magic is "
"powerful on the front lines, if we’re ever struggling it’s also important "
"that I have the chance to recruit new magi from our keep."
msgstr ""
"Wir haben eine beträchtliche Menge Gold angesammelt, Lehrling. Während meine "
"Magie an der Front mächtig ist, ist es auch wichtig, dass ich, falls wir "
"einmal in Bedrängnis geraten, die Möglichkeit habe, von unserem Burgfried "
"aus neue Magier auszubilden."

#. [message]
#. Ozgob has died, and any remaining goblins are deserting him
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/01_Stirrings_of_War.cfg:616
msgid "Run away!"
msgstr "Lauft weg!"

#. [message]: speaker=Ozgob
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/01_Stirrings_of_War.cfg:621
msgid "Useless... goblins..."
msgstr "Nutzlose… Kobolde…"

#. [message]: speaker=Garard
#. King Garard has just appeared, along with a few knights
#. King Garard has just appeared, along with a few knights
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/01_Stirrings_of_War.cfg:641
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/01_Stirrings_of_War.cfg:679
msgid ""
"Ride forth, knights of Wesnoth! No orc who sets foot on our soil shall leave "
"alive!"
msgstr ""
"Reitet aus, Ritter von Wesnoth! Kein Ork, der unseren Boden betritt, darf "
"lebend entkommen!"

#. [message]: speaker=Garard
#. Garard came to kill the goblins, but Delfador has already done it.
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/01_Stirrings_of_War.cfg:649
msgid ""
"But what’s this? It seems some magi have beaten us to battle and already "
"slain our foe! I wasn’t making a mistake bringing Alduin into the fold after "
"all. Who commands this detachment?"
msgstr ""
"Aber was ist das? Es scheint, als seien uns einige Magier zuvorgekommen und "
"hätten unseren Feind bereits niedergemacht! Anscheinend war es kein Fehler, "
"Alduin mit einzubeziehen. Wer führt diesen Trupp?"

#. [message]: speaker=Methor
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/01_Stirrings_of_War.cfg:653
msgid ""
"(bowing) My Lord, Alduin dispatched these apprentices as response to your "
"war-call. I volunteered to lead them, and I now place my medicinal arts at "
"your service."
msgstr ""
"(verbeugt sich) Mein Herr, Alduin entsandte diese Lehrlinge als Antwort auf "
"Euren Ruf zu den Waffen. Ich meldete mich freiwillig, sie zu führen, und "
"stelle nun meine heilkundigen Künste in Euren Dienst."

#. [message]: speaker=Garard
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/01_Stirrings_of_War.cfg:657
msgid ""
"A healer? Well, we’ll have need of your services soon enough. Follow me back "
"to camp. We attack on the morrow!"
msgstr ""
"Ein Heiler? Nun, wir werden Eurer Dienste bald genug bedürfen. Folgt mir "
"zurück ins Lager. Wir greifen morgen an!"

#. [message]: speaker=Garard
#. Delfador has failed to defeat the goblins. Garard does not respect him.
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/01_Stirrings_of_War.cfg:687
msgid ""
"But what’s this? Some pencil-necked magi have beaten us to battle, yet can’t "
"even finish off a few goblins! Bah, go back to Alduin, you scholars have no "
"place in war after all."
msgstr ""
"Aber was ist das? Ein paar stümperhafte Magier haben sich in die Schlacht "
"gestürzt, und konnten es nicht einmal mit ein paar Kobolden aufnehmen! Bah, "
"schert Euch schnell zurück nach Alduin. Ihr Schreibstubenhelden habt im "
"Krieg eben doch nichts verloren."

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/01_Stirrings_of_War.cfg:691
msgid "Now I’ll never make a name for myself..."
msgstr "Nun werde ich mir nie einen Namen machen…"

#. [scenario]: id=02_Fort_Garard
#. [side]: type=Halberdier, id=Luraery
#. [side]: type=Lieutenant, id=Aelyn
#. [side]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/02_Fort_Garard.cfg:6
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/12_The_Traitor.cfg:68
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/12_The_Traitor.cfg:87
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/12_The_Traitor.cfg:102
msgid "Fort Garard"
msgstr "Festung Garard"

