#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/utils/macros.cfg:479
msgid "Kraa!"
msgstr "Kraa!"

#. [message]: speaker={UNIT}
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/utils/macros.cfg:488
msgid "Glob glob glob."
msgstr "Gluck gluck gluck."

#. [message]: speaker={UNIT}
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/utils/macros.cfg:497
msgid "Fsss crackle hiss."
msgstr "Fsss knister zischel."

#. [object]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/utils/spellcasting.cfg:80
msgid "missile"
msgstr "Geschoss"

#. [floating_text]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/utils/spellcasting.cfg:239
msgid "No Target"
msgstr "Kein Ziel"

#. [dummy]: id=panacea
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/utils/spellcasting.cfg:286
msgid "panacea"
msgstr "Wunderheilung"

#. [dummy]: id=panacea
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/utils/spellcasting.cfg:287
msgid "Next turn, this unit dies."
msgstr "Diese Einheit stirbt in der nächsten Runde."

#. [leadership]: id=summoner
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/utils/spellcasting.cfg:370
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/utils/spellcasting.cfg:1737
msgid "summoner"
msgstr "Beschwörer"

#. [leadership]: id=summoner
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/utils/spellcasting.cfg:371
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/utils/spellcasting.cfg:1738
msgid ""
"This unit is a skilled summoner. Adjacent allied elementals deal +100% "
"damage and gain +100% experience.\n"
"\n"
"Recruited elementals dissipate at the end of each scenario."
msgstr ""
"Diese Einheit ist ein geübter Beschwörer. Benachbarte verbündete Elementare "
"verursachen +100% Schaden und erhalten +100% Erfahrung.\n"
"\n"
"Rekrutierte Elementare verflüchtigen sich am Ende jedes Szenarios."

#. [object]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/utils/spellcasting.cfg:461
msgid "chill touch"
msgstr "Eiskalte Hand"

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/utils/spellcasting.cfg:528
msgid ""
"My levitate spell has ended over impassable terrain! I‘m falling to my death!"
msgstr ""
"Mein Flugzauber ist über unpassierbarem Gelände zu Ende gegangen! Ich werde "
"in den Tod stürzen!"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/utils/spellcasting.cfg:607
msgid "Familiar"
msgstr "Vertrauter"

#. [message]: speaker=Methor
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/utils/spellcasting.cfg:642
msgid ""
"A familiar already, apprentice? Well done — that’s an impressive piece of "
"magic even for experienced wizards."
msgstr ""
"Jetzt schon ein Vertrauter, mein Schüler? Gut gemacht — dies ist ein "
"beeindruckendes magisches Kunststück, selbst für einen erfahrenen Zauberer."

#. [dummy]: id=mnemonic
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/utils/spellcasting.cfg:661
msgid "mnemonic"
msgstr "Schnellmerker"

#. [dummy]: id=mnemonic
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/utils/spellcasting.cfg:662
msgid "Whenever an adjacent ally gains xp, you gain the same amount of xp."
msgstr ""
"Immer wenn ein benachbarter Verbündeter EP erhält, erhaltet Ihr dieselbe "
"Menge EP."

#. [disable]: id=skill_counterspell
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/utils/spellcasting.cfg:1028
msgid "counterspelled"
msgstr "Gegenzauber"

#. [disable]: id=skill_counterspell
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/utils/spellcasting.cfg:1029
msgid "Counterspell is nullifying this magical attack."
msgstr "Der Gegenzauber lässt die Wirkung dieses magischen Angriffs verpuffen."

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#. Delfador has just cast his Counterspell spell. Magical attacks (including Delfador's) are disabled when near Delfador
#. explicitly make this a Delfador invention (with a bit of self-fulfilling/recursive prophecy to boot). Don't want counterspell messing up the universe at large
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/utils/spellcasting.cfg:1073
msgid ""
"They called me crazy, but I always knew I could figure out a way to block "
"magic! I just needed to copy what I— the fake I— did during that prophecy."
msgstr ""
"Sie hielten mich für verrückt, doch ich wusste immer, dass ich einen Weg "
"finden würde, Magie zu blockieren! Ich musste nur nachahmen, was ich – das "
"andere Ich – während jener Prophezeiung getan hat."

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/utils/spellcasting.cfg:1297
msgid ""
"My polymorph spell has ended over impassable terrain! I‘m falling to my "
"death!"
msgstr ""
"Mein Verwandlungszauber ist über unpassierbarem Gelände zu Ende gegangen! "
"Ich werde in den Tod stürzen!"

#. [object]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/utils/spellcasting.cfg:1393
msgid "dancing daggers"
msgstr "Tanzende Dolche"

#. [chance_to_hit]: id=skill_illusion
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/utils/spellcasting.cfg:1463
msgid "accuracy:"
msgstr "Genauigkeit:"

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#. Delfador is magically disguised as a drake, and has just case a fireball
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/utils/spellcasting.cfg:1600
msgid "Taste drakefire!"
msgstr "Schmecke Drakenfeuer!"

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#. Delfador has just saved a unit from lethal damage with the Contingency spell
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/utils/spellcasting.cfg:1819
msgid "I’ve got you! You can thank my old master for inventing this spell."
msgstr ""
"Ihr seid gerettet! Ihr könnt meinem alten Meister danken, der diesen Spruch "
"einst erfand."

#. [message]: speaker=Methor
#. Methor is probably not here right now to say this line, but he might be
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/utils/spellcasting.cfg:1824
msgid "Well, somebody had to! And you’re welcome!"
msgstr "Einer musste es ja tun! Gern geschehen!"

#. [object]: type=fire
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/utils/spellcasting.cfg:1884
msgid "lightning"
msgstr "Blitz"

#. [dummy]: id=chain
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/utils/spellcasting.cfg:1894
msgid "chain"
msgstr "Ketten"

#. [dummy]: id=chain
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/utils/spellcasting.cfg:1895
msgid ""
"This attack can be used multiple times on offense, but consecutive uses "
"strike one fewer time."
msgstr ""
"Dieser Angriff kann in einem Zug mehrfach eingesetzt werden, trifft bei "
"aufeinanderfolgenden Einsätzen jedoch jeweils einmal weniger."

#. [message]: speaker=$speaker_id
#. Delfador has just cast his cataclysm spell, dealing heavy damage in a large radius and destroying trees/villages/castles
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/utils/spellcasting.cfg:2204
msgid "Dear lords of light, what demon has come upon us?!"
msgstr ""
"Oh gesegnete Götter des Lichts, welche dämonischen Kräfte wurden hier "
"entfesselt?!"

#. [set_menu_item]: id=TDG_spellcasting
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/utils/spellcasting.cfg:2494
msgid "Cast Spells"
msgstr "Zauber wirken"

#. [floating_text]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/utils/spellcasting.cfg:2532
msgid "Max XP!"
msgstr "Max. EP!"

#. [message]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/utils/spellcasting.cfg:2544
msgid ""
"Unlike regular units, the apprentice does not use XP to advance, and will "
"instead advance automatically over time as he progresses through the story. "
"The apprentice’s XP is useful for casting spells, but raising him to maximum "
"XP has no special effect."
msgstr ""
"Im Gegensatz zu gewöhnlichen Einheiten nutzt der Lehrling EP nicht zum "
"Aufstieg, sondern steigt im Verlauf der Geschichte automatisch auf. Die EP "
"des Lehrlings sind zum Wirken von Zaubern nützlich, doch ihn auf maximale EP "
"zu bringen hat keinen besonderen Effekt."

#. [message]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/utils/spellcasting.cfg:2554
msgid ""
"Unlike regular units, Delfador does not use XP to advance, and will instead "
"advance automatically over time as he progresses through the story. "
"Delfador’s XP is useful for casting spells, but raising him to maximum XP "
"has no special effect."
msgstr ""
"Im Gegensatz zu gewöhnlichen Einheiten nutzt Delfador EP nicht zum Aufstieg, "
"sondern steigt im Verlauf der Geschichte automatisch auf. Delfadors EP sind "
"zum Wirken von Zaubern nützlich, doch ihn auf maximale EP zu bringen hat "
"keinen besonderen Effekt."

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/utils/spellcasting.cfg:2570
msgid ""
"Congratulations on your journeymanship, $unit.name! Those fireballs are "
"breathtaking! ...now how long until I’m allowed to cast them too?"
msgstr ""
"Glückwunsch zur Gesellenprüfung, $unit.name! Diese Feuerbälle sind "
"atemberaubend! …wie lange wohl noch, bis ich sie auch wirken darf?"

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/utils/spellcasting.cfg:2581
msgid ""
"Congratulations, $unit.name! Your journeyman’s robes look breathtaking. Now "
"if only Methor would award me mine too ...in red, of course."
msgstr ""
"Glückwunsch, $unit.name! Eure Gesellenrobe sieht atemberaubend aus. Wenn "
"Methor mir doch auch endlich meine verleihen würde …in Rot natürlich."

#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/utils/unified_characters.cfg:54
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/utils/unified_characters.cfg:66
