msgstr "Methor"

#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/utils/unified_characters.cfg:92
msgid "Arand"
msgstr "Arand"

#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/utils/unified_characters.cfg:105
msgid "Asheviere"
msgstr "Asheviere"

#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/utils/unified_characters.cfg:144
msgid "Lionel"
msgstr "Lionel"

#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/utils/unified_characters.cfg:162
msgid "Lord Maddock"
msgstr "Lord Maddock"

#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/utils/unified_characters.cfg:174
msgid "Colonel Dommel"
msgstr "Oberst Dommel"

#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/utils/unified_characters.cfg:186
msgid "Kestrel"
msgstr "Kestrel"

#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/utils/unified_characters.cfg:222
msgid "Iliah-Malal"
msgstr "Iliah-Malal"

#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/utils/unified_characters.cfg:261
msgid "Garard II"
msgstr "Garard II."

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/utils/unified_characters.cfg:564
msgid "No, it can’t end yet! I have so much left to do..."
msgstr "Nein, es darf noch nicht zu Ende gehen! Ich habe noch so viel zu tun…"

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/utils/unified_characters.cfg:575
msgid "No! Magic, why have you failed me..."
msgstr "Nein! Magie, warum hast du mich verlassen…"

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/utils/unified_characters.cfg:586
msgid "If only I had been a little wiser..."
msgstr "Wenn ich nur etwas mehr Weisheit besessen hätte…"

#. [message]: speaker=Methor
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/utils/unified_characters.cfg:598
msgid "War, pain, death... I tried so hard to change things..."
msgstr "Krieg, Schmerz, Tod… ich habe versucht, die Dinge zu ändern…"

#. [message]: speaker=Deoran
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/utils/unified_characters.cfg:610
msgid "I have failed my kingdom and my duty..."
msgstr "Ich habe mein Königreich und meine Pflicht enttäuscht…"

#. [message]: speaker=Garard
#. reference to Shakespeare's Richard III
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/utils/unified_characters.cfg:622
msgid "A horse! A horse! My kingdom for a horse..."
msgstr "Ein Pferd! Ein Pferd! Mein Königreich für ein Pferd…"

#. [message]: speaker=Asheviere
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/utils/unified_characters.cfg:632
msgid "It’s finally over..."
msgstr "Endlich ist es vorbei…"

#. [message]: speaker=Lionel
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/utils/unified_characters.cfg:642
msgid "Blasted orcs..."
msgstr "Verfluchte Orks…"

#. [message]: speaker=Kalenz
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/utils/unified_characters.cfg:654
msgid "Nobody can cheat death forever..."
msgstr "Niemand kann dem Tod für alle Zeit entrinnen…"

#. [message]: speaker=Chantal
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/utils/unified_characters.cfg:665
msgid "Deoran, I never had a chance to tell you—"
msgstr "Deoran, ich habe es nie geschafft, dir zu sagen…"

#. [message]: speaker=Lynyan
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/utils/unified_characters.cfg:680
msgid "Boss, I ain’t feelin’ too hot..."
msgstr "Boss, ich fühl' mich nich' so prickelnd…"

#. [message]: speaker=Lynyan
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/utils/unified_characters.cfg:685
msgid "I ain’t feelin’ too hot..."
msgstr "Ich fühl' mich nich' so prickelnd…"

#. [message]: speaker=Barin
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/utils/unified_characters.cfg:696
msgid "I shoulda never left my swamp..."
msgstr "Hätt ich bloß meinen Sumpf niemals verlassen…"

#. [message]: speaker=Kaylan
#. since he reappears in HttT's blackwater port, he can't die here.
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/utils/unified_characters.cfg:706
msgid ""
"I am grievously injured; I can be of no further aid in your quest. Fight on "
"without me, Delfador!"
msgstr ""
"Meine Verletzungen sind zu schwer; ich würde Euch in Eurer Quest eher eine "
"Last denn eine Hilfe sein. Kämpft ohne mich weiter, Delfador!"
